title: Danielle Staub takes shots at Dolores Catania and Siggy Flicker, sides with Margaret Josephs

meta_data.description: Danielle Staub has taken sides on RHONJ against Siggy Flicker and Dolores Catania and even used her recent blog post to tear them down even more.
